	* config/loongarch/loongarch-driver.h (ASM_MRELAX_DEFAULT):
	Define.
	(ASM_MRELAX_SPEC): Define.
	(ASM_SPEC): Use ASM_MRELAX_SPEC instead of "%{mno-relax}".
	* config/loongarch/loongarch.cc: Take the setting of
